<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>وَمُقَابِله تصح ويراعى تَرْتِيب نَفسه<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span>فصل فِي بَقِيَّة شُرُوط الْقدْوَة<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
